videos.headline: Crosby: Fleury was 'huge for us all series long'
videos.description: Sidney Crosby explains how Marc-Andre Fleury stepped up in the series against the Capitals, helping the Penguins advance to the Eastern Conference finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Presser (Crosby: Fleury was 'huge for us all series long') 2017/05/10 SC

videos.headline: Melrose breaks down Pittsburgh's Game 7 victory
videos.description: Barry Melrose says Pittsburgh "played a perfect road game" and did a great job of limiting Washington's speed in the neutral zone en route to a 2-0 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose breaks down Pittsburgh's Game 7 victory) 2017/05/10 SC
